title: The James Brown Theory DVD - 2009 Release
description:
THE JAMES BROWN THEORY


A collage documentary on the Hardest Working Man in Showbiz, the God Father Of Soul.  



*Prior to making this DVD, I had absolutely no experience or training in video production.  I made it with a free program called DVD Flick.  Finding all the video clips (38 included, many not) and organizing the dvd structure was the easier part.  Converting all the files (no matter how hard I tried, always errors) and authoring a dvd proved the most difficult aspect of this project.  No wonder studio execs have so many assistants running around; to do all the dirty work!*





Be Free
